Package: cleanR
Title: Data Cleaning Tools for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Steven", "Nanga", email = "stephennanga97@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A collection of tools for data cleaning in R. This package provides 
    functions for removing duplicates, standardizing categorical variables, 
    converting data types, and removing outliers. It aims to streamline the 
    data cleaning process by offering a unified interface for common data 
    preparation tasks.
